channel.title: WAYHI [317] (My First Server)
channel.description:
Hi guys I'm new here and thought to contribute to the community so I can hopefully make some friends, so I invted "WAYHI", which is a 317 server. Me taking a class at school in Java right now, I decided to make something and like said, upload it.
Please tell me what you think and if you have any questions plz add me on skype guys: char18f1397
Thanks!
THE SERVER:
Features: ● 602 Anims + GFX ● 602 NPCS ● 634 Items ● Summoning Pets ● Perfect Pking System ● Fixed Corp ● Fixed Term ● Working Prayer ● Player Kill Yell Ranking ● Working Slayer Task's and points. ● Working Mage Points. ● Fixed Teleblock. ● Fixed Dupe Bug. ● Moved Shops. ● Change Donator Commands. [size=24pt]SOME PICS :)[/size] [img]http://i1214.photobucket.com/albums/cc492/317Delta/sclol.jpg[/img] [img]http://i1214.photobucket.com/albums/cc492/317Delta/td.jpg[/img] [img]http://i1214.photobucket.com/albums/cc492/317Delta/tbfix.jpg[/img] [img]http://i1214.photobucket.com/albums/cc492/317Delta/corp.jpg[/img] [img]http://i1214.photobucket.com/albums/cc492/317Delta/ptay.jpg[/img] [img]http://i1214.photobucket.com/albums/cc492/317Delta/eqstats.jpg[/img]
DOWNLOAD :D :D :D DOWNLOAD HERE: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?rk832sw8qc6ka6a]http://www.mediafire.com/?rk832sw8qc6ka6a[/url]
[size=36pt]CREDITS[/size] I'd like to especially thank my teacher, Mr. Ramazyck, for teaching me how to code in Java. I can make make some pretty neat stuff thanks to his time, help, & effort! :D
